Tully Marshall https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tully_Marshall 0 Tully Marshall (born William Phillips, April 10, 1864 – March 10, 1943) was an American character actor. He had nearly a quarter century of theatrical experience before his debut film appearance in 1914.
